body_html:
I think the problem is the URL 'https://boringssl.googlesource.com/boringssl/' is not work for me, since I am not using tensorflow distributed currently, I set "option(tensorflow_ENABLE_GRPC_SUPPORT "Enable gRPC support" OFF)" in the file "tensorflow/tensorflow/contrib/cmake/CMakeLists.txt", and then CMake and build again. It is compiled success now.
thanks for your help! @snnn

body:
I think the problem is the URL 'https://boringssl.googlesource.com/boringssl/' is not work for me, since I am not using tensorflow distributed currently, I set "option(tensorflow_ENABLE_GRPC_SUPPORT "Enable gRPC support" OFF)" in the file "tensorflow/tensorflow/contrib/cmake/CMakeLists.txt", and then CMake and build again. It is compiled success now.
thanks for your help! @snnn
